{"tid":2111060,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自家製乾式熟成帶骨肉眼 Dry age bone in Ribeye + 是日晚餐","createTime":"2020-07-16T09:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T04:11:41.000Z","uid":260581,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"40204f5b8b5b23fea0ba2437744b7ba81a6bd1e9","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"大家好 大概一個月前<br />\n我係米國訂左呢個umai bag<br />\n佢係一個特殊袋 令你可以係屋企都dry age到<br />\n咁就早幾日到貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gvxgr7j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvxgr7j.jpg&h=c9b57acc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEKKA0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEKKA0F.jpg&h=b3f91d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袋入面有3個dry age袋, 5塊adapter strips用黎真空完封袋用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPRw0tT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPRw0tT.jpg&h=bf014765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我買左呢舊5.3kg 帶骨肉眼 接近$1500 HKD<br />\n呢舊係第一舊熟成肉 我都驚會收舊肉皮<br />\n舊肉望落油花麻麻 所以冇影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我本身想買既有少少出入 佢切走曬d fat cap<br />\n但我見佢真空左俾我就算 冇出聲換到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmNzYhi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmNzYhi.jpg&h=90d408fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9R82J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9R82J0.jpg&h=a3c223aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先要洗一洗舊肉個真空袋<br />\n之後準備一個乾淨既field 同將umai袋摺起袋口<br />\n<br />\n之後就要戴手套 係唔掂舊肉既情況下<br />\n將兩個袋connect 然後將舊肉轉袋<br />\n但我初體驗 肉又太大 最後都係用手掂左舊肉先放到落袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我帶住手套 一個人整好煩<br />\n所以影唔到所有step<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92JLkxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92JLkxd.jpg&h=07c0b3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcYfHLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcYfHLz.jpg&h=b10a0b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後就貼label 同放兩塊strips 抽真空封袋口 <br />\n個袋唔係真空袋 所以唔洗抽曬d空氣出黎<br />\n呢舊肉咁大 我會dry age佢45日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzQUYjJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzQUYjJ.jpg&h=a55c02a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整之前先洗一洗雪櫃<br />\n放係上層 等到829就有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望舊肉唔會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n829就dry age第二舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次第一舊就當練習 下次買舊好d既黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c488c8ecd29581c1481b1332717116bc190d1d","tid":2111060,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35ab0a1aa51be214bd00dd976d01bd0dc8c2d6a","tid":2111060,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dry age"},{"pid":"76cb40eae4ca1fc1b681b3e02fd0c124f099253c","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"是日晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iPhTvsM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiPhTvsM.jpg&h=18679a63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dspCcF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdspCcF7.jpg&h=b441c520&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ax1Eq08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax1Eq08.jpg&h=ed9adc14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqMMQsP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqMMQsP.jpg&h=a2023766&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRf551b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRf551b.jpg&h=7127a5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VC02oNS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVC02oNS.jpg&h=030a7e02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWifJNT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWifJNT.jpg&h=becf2b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n骨髓就先用鹽水放雪櫃浸一晚<br />\n用刀清一清個底<br />\n我有一條刮左用黎 撈左少少蒜 芫荽莖 鹽黑胡椒調味<br />\n另一條就用 鹽 黑胡椒 蒜粉調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad0a5c6f9fb0d3fd201bec9f3af5caa5aea881d","tid":2111060,"uid":313546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"屋企用個袋係雪櫃dryage完 個雪櫃會唔會有味？ 同埋雪櫃其他野嘅味走唔走到入去？<br />\n之前一直都想試 但係又怕雪櫃臭"},{"pid":"7df3e9757d2a50e3667b542f7cd3dfdbe4a52d1f","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c488c8ecd29581c1481b1332717116bc190d1d","tid":2111060,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"千呼萬喚 希望唔好收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85d0642a8cdb4faa4003ce619420c97609a9c71","tid":2111060,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a2c5ebcab6d4b21795313bad5b17eaa60adf46","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad0a5c6f9fb0d3fd201bec9f3af5caa5aea881d","tid":2111060,"uid":313546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"屋企用個袋係雪櫃dryage完 個雪櫃會唔會有味？ 同埋雪櫃其他野嘅味走唔走到入去？<br />\n之前一直都想試 但係又怕雪櫃臭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"我都係第一次整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過應該唔會 我見上網冇人講過有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2223a8ecb2146836772dfb6be8f6eda6555eea","tid":2111060,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"乾式熟成好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d7076251e7d60151e523a7215af0ee65231091","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e35ab0a1aa51be214bd00dd976d01bd0dc8c2d6a","tid":2111060,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dry age"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"初體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fb25d78085e35586a6a69b100af9b08ba0688e","tid":2111060,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"好撚正窮撚好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592ac933ae354aad69187dff56bb249e030964fb","tid":2111060,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df3e9757d2a50e3667b542f7cd3dfdbe4a52d1f","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c488c8ecd29581c1481b1332717116bc190d1d","tid":2111060,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"千呼萬喚 希望唔好收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"一個人食哂 bone marrow<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c907a97f8984351b59ceba2c4a322dbce394e57a","tid":2111060,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d90fac8ceba2daf253aaa93e5b81b02ecbe1efd","tid":2111060,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85d0642a8cdb4faa4003ce619420c97609a9c71","tid":2111060,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"多謝小fatby欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a22c1df1837fc95b849b20b72d4d8ad99a9